description: Gavin Waters and Nikko Alexander take on Trent Diesel and Matthew Singer in a brutally hot balls-to-the-wall tag team match in front of a live audience this week on NK. These four big dicked muscle studs have all proven their wrestling skills and earned top spots on the NK feeding chain. Now they fight it out for the right to totally humiliate, dominate and fuck the losers in front of a cheering crowd of their fans. Who will proudly come out on top and who will be on the bottom and have their hole violated and pounded?
title: Gavin Waters & Nikko Alexander vs Trent Diesel & Matthew Singer
